# WF-MR-03 | M+R Audit PDF Assembly & Delivery
## Handoff Guide

---

## 01 — Purpose

WF-MR-03 is the final workflow in the M+R Audit pipeline. Its sole responsibility is assembling the populated PDF report and making it available for download. It does not generate any GPT content — that work is complete when this workflow fires. WF-MR-03 reads, assembles, stores, and delivers.

**Inputs:** A completed `assessment_id` with WF-MR-01 and WF-MR-02 both confirmed complete.

**Output:** A populated PDF file stored in Supabase Storage with a signed URL written to `gm_report_artifacts`, accessible from the dashboard "Download Full Report" button.

---

