## 09 — Guardrails

**Do NOT:**
- Modify `vw_mr_gpt_inputs`, WF-MR-01, or WF-MR-02 in any way
- Store the PDF binary in `gm_report_artifacts` — store only the storage path and signed URL
- Leave the populated Google Doc copy in Drive after successful PDF upload
- Skip the WF-MR-01 and WF-MR-02 completion checks — generating a report before synthesis is complete will produce a document full of empty merge tokens

**Must:**
- Verify all column names in `vw_mr_report_payload` match template tokens exactly before building Node 10
- Use `upsert: true` on the Storage upload to allow clean re-generation
- Handle the signed URL expiry case — either re-generate on demand or set a sufficiently long expiry window
- Connect error outputs from all Google API nodes — these are the most likely failure points

